*	|----------------------------|
*	|	Enable   |		D2		 |
*	|	Step     |		D3		 |
*	|	Dir      |		D4		 |
*	|	GND      |		GND		 |
*	------------------------------	
*
*
*		ATTENTION: There is a 10 second delay from powering up uStepper to accepting input - this is to avoid movement on control jitter when CNC/Printer board starts up !
*
*/
